<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="G" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Gale" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Gale,</orth> a moderate wind: <cit><quote>auspicious --s,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tmp 5.314" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. V, 314</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>happy g.</quote> <bibl n="shak. shr 1.2.48" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. I, 2, 48</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>a little g.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 3h6 5.3.10" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C V, 3, 10</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>every g. and vary of their masters,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lr 2.2.85" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. II, 2, 85</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>